title: I Can Summon God
description: I Can Summon God ManhuaTraversed and became the demoted prince, fortunately God did not let Qin Jun despair, activate the myth system! All characters in mythology can be summoned! The Monkey King who can shake the mountains and rivers with one stick! Clairvoyance and ears, insight into the world! Buddha that holds people in the palm of hand, and no one can escape! In this world of demons and gods, I vowed to be the strongest god emperor! I Have Summoned All Kind of Gods and Demons I Can Summon God 我召唤出了诸天神魔
